QString Settings::getPDFPaperSizeWidth (   )  const
 

Get the default PDF paper size width.

This value will be a decimal number (ie, "10.0") that corresponds to Settings::getPDFPaperSizeUnits().

Note:
This value only makes sense if Settings::getPDFPaperSizeInt() == 3
